<m0>Medical mystery deepens<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 1 IS 2.73 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   HEAD DEPTH TO THIS POINT IS .890 INCHES<m2><ql>
<m0>Recovery spurs suspicions girl was abused, not ill<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS 1.299 INCHES<m2><ql>
<ql>
<m1><styl>cxoff<ql>
<styl>RULERON<ql>
